00:20:23.820 --> 00:20:25.650
So I mentioned the
metadata standard.

00:20:25.650 --> 00:20:27.380
This is a really
important thing for us,

00:20:27.380 --> 00:20:28.870
and it's been a huge success.

00:20:28.870 --> 00:20:31.050
We didn't want this to just
be a closed thing, where

00:20:31.050 --> 00:20:33.670
